  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl31_LabelType\">You grew up and were raised around fabulous sporting events, and your youth was consumed with a driving need to be better than everyone else. Any hint of a contest spurs you to your greatest heights of potential.</span></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl31_LabelType\">Whenever another creature within 30 feet attempts a skill check and you attempt a check with the same skill before the start of that creature&rsquo;s next turn, you gain a +1 trait bonus on your check (this includes attempting an opposed skill check against the creature).</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl31_LabelType\"><strong>Suggested Characters</strong></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl31_LabelType\">Brevans, Kurgess worshipers, Sargavans.</span></p>",
